  "description": "A cinematic organ-pad tone with a very slow ageRate — the note starts pristine and over 30+ seconds develops warmth and gentle transformer corrosion. The long sediment reverb tail turns the room itself into an aging chamber. Perfect for film scoring tension beds.",
